<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>가산대학교 교직원지원시스템</title>

    <style>
        body{
            /* font-weight:300; */
            font-size:15px;
            color:#333333;
        }
        .top-left-header{
            width: 100%;
            height: 50px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            left: 0;
            background-color: #003875;
            padding: 5px 5px 5px 0px;
        }
        .top-left-header ul{
            list-style: none;
        }
        .top-left-header ul li{
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid white;
            padding-left: 5px;
        }
        .top-left-header ul li a{
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo{
            float: left;
            margin-right: 100px;
        }

        .main-ul{
            list-style: none;
        }
        .sub-ul{
            list-style: none;
        }
        .main-ul > li{
            float:left;
            position:relative;
            margin:30px 0 0 0;
            text-align:center;
            padding:0 1.5%;}
        .main-ul > li > a{
            padding: 30px 0 26px 0;
            font-weight:400;font-size:20px;color:#333333; text-decoration: none;}
        .main-ul > li > a:hover{color:#134c8b;font-weight:500;}
        .sub-ul{
            display:none;
            padding:10px 0 20px 5px;opacity: 0.8;background-color: #003876;width: 180px;position: absolute;top:50px;left: -40px;text-align: left;}
        .sub-ul li{padding:10px 20px 0;}
        .sub-ul li a{font-size:15px;color:#ffffff; text-decoration: none;}
        .sub-ul li a:hover{
            color:#cdcdcd;
            text-decoration:underline;}
        .main-ul li:hover .sub-ul{display: block;}
        .main-ul li:active .sub-ul{display: block;}
        footer{
            border-top: 1px solid #cdcdcd;
        }
        footer ul{
            list-style: none;
            color: #333333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <header>
        <div class="top-left-header">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">처음으로</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">로그아웃</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="logo">
            <h1><img src="kasanlogo2.jpg" alt="KASAN UNIVERSITY" >
                교직원지원시스템</h1>
        </div>
       
       <nav>
        <ul class="main-ul">
            <li><a href="#">신상정보</a>
                <ul class="sub-ul">
                    <li><a href="#">개인신상조회</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">학생조회</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><a href="#">수업</a>
                <ul class="sub-ul">
                    <li><a href="#">강좌조회</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">시간표조회</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><a href="#">성적</a>
                <ul class="sub-ul">
                    <li><a href="#">현학기 성적조회</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">전체 성적조회</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">성적입력 및 수정</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li><a href="#">게시판</a>
                <ul class="sub-ul">
                    <li><a href="#">공지사항</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">자유게시판</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

        	
    </header>
    <img src="main2.jpg" alt="" width="100%" >
    <h2>공지사항</h2>
    <footer>
        <ul>
            <li>부산 부산진구 중앙대로 688</li>
            <li>TEL : 051-912-1000</li>
            <li>copyrights (C) KASAN UNIVERSITY. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED</li>
        </ul>
    </footer>
    
</body>
</html>
